OL,3,CVoters in the North West have their
OL,4,Csay ahead of local elections
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports' Political
OL,7,FCorrespondent Lise McNally spoke to
OL,8,Flocal voters in Heaton Park in
OL,9,FManchester ahead of the local
OL,10,Felections.
OL,12,FPeople across the North West will head
OL,13,Fto the polls on Thursday 7 May, but
OL,14,Fmany people are split on whether to
OL,15,Fvote based on national or local
OL,16,Fpolitics, or even vote at all.
OL,18,F21 council areas will have seats up
OL,19,Ffor grabs, with 1/3 councillors to be
OL,20,Felected across all 10 boroughs in
OL,21,FGreater Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
