OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776445554
OL,3,CVoters in the North West have their
OL,4,Csay ahead of local elections
OL,6,F"The state of the roads are appalling
OL,7,Fand I know a lot of people who live
OL,8,Faround me are quite passionate about
OL,9,Fthat, also investment. I know we've
OL,10,Fhad some investment in local leisure
OL,11,Ffacilities."
OL,13,FProfessor Jon Tonge - a politics
OL,14,Fprofessor from the University of
OL,15,FLiverpool - said: "Some people will
OL,16,Fvote on local issues, some people on
OL,17,Fnational issues.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
