PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776445554
OL,3,CVoters in the North West have their
OL,4,Csay ahead of local elections
OL,6,F"This will tell us whether Labour is
OL,7,Fon course for another term at the next
OL,8,FGeneral Election, this will tell us
OL,9,Fwhether there's a revival under Kemi
OL,10,FBadenoch, it will tell us how the
OL,11,FLiberal Democrats are doing, and it
OL,12,Fwill tell us how the Greens and Reform
OL,13,FUK are doing."
OL,15,FSmaller and independent parties have
OL,16,Fbeen making gains since the last
OL,17,FGeneral Election in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
