OL,3,CVoters in the North West have their
OL,4,Csay ahead of local elections
OL,6,FThe Green Party won their fifth seat
OL,7,Fin the Commons when Hannah Spencer won
OL,8,Fthe Gorton and Denton by-election in
OL,9,FFebruary 2026. The seat had previously
OL,10,Fbeen a Labour safe-seat, but ended up
OL,11,Fa race between the Greens and Reform
OL,12,FUK.
OL,14,FReform UK also won a by-election in
OL,15,FMay 2025, when Sarah Pochin won in
OL,16,FRuncorn and Helsby by just six votes.
OL,18,FOne woman told ITV News that she does
OL,19,Fnot feel excited by the local
OL,20,Felections.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
