OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776445554
OL,3,CVoters in the North West have their
OL,4,Csay ahead of local elections
OL,6,FShe said: "I'd like to see them do
OL,7,Fmore for communities. It's just not
OL,8,Fenough and nobody seems to listen".
OL,10,FAnother woman said the biggest issue
OL,11,Fshe will be looking out for is
OL,12,Fchildcare and access to jobs for
OL,13,Fsingle parents, while another said
OL,14,Fthat while she has received campaign
OL,15,Fleaflets, she does not know who to
OL,16,Fvote for.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
